AlphaMail,is,a,cloud,based,transactional,email,service,that,makes,it,easier,for,developers,and,marketing,professionals,to,utilize,transactional,email,in,their,daily,work,Users,can,stop,worrying,about,maintaining,their,own,infrastructure,and,let,AlphaMail,provide,high,deliverability,dynamic,templates,and,real,time,statistics,AlphaMail,offers,a,RESTful,API,for,programmatic,access,to,AlphaMail,services,API,methods,include,Email,Queue,Projects,Templates,and,Signatures,An,API,key,is,required